query:
SELECT c.nome, f.dataFesta, DATE_FORMAT(f.dataFesta, '%Y-%m-%d %H:%i:%s') as formatted, f.codigo
FROM festas f
JOIN clientes c ON f.clienteId = c.id
WHERE c.nome LIKE '%Rodrigo%'
LIMIT 1
